node.text:
🍁🍐🍎DUMB FRUIT 7🍎🍐🍁

Available in 4pks at both taprooms starting today! Or you can order online for Ridgewood pickup or shipping in qualifying states.

DUMB FRUIT 7 - APPLE, PEAR, CRANBERRY, MAPLE
Sour Ale / 6.6% / Looking forward to autumn with some apple, pear, and cranberry with maple to top it off. Crisp, juicy, sweet.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by EVIL TWIN BREWING NYC in Evil Twin Brewing. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Milky Way & Back VI is definitely one of the best in the series 🍒 Drops tomorrow at noon along with the others listed below!

TO THE MILKY WAY & BACK VI - RASPBERRY, CHERRY, WHITE CHOCOLATE
Milkshake IPA / 7.5% / Drinks like a chocolate-berry milkshake. Smoothie-like, juicy, sweet. Contains milk sugar.
$22/4pk

DUMB FRUIT 7 - APPLE, PEAR, CRANBERRY, MAPLE
Sour Ale / 6.6% / Looking forward to autumn with some apple, pear, and cranberry with maple to top it off. Crisp, juicy, sweet.
$24/4pk

I THINK I’VE SAID THE WORDS BUSHWICK AND RAVES TOO MUCH BC I KEEP GETTING ADS FOR CHEAP BEER
Triple IPA / 10% / Double dry-hopped with Citra, El Dorado, and Galaxy hops. Distinct aromas of grapefruit, passion fruit, and orange zest.
$22/4pk

EVIL WATER - PINK PINEAPPLE
Hard Seltzer / 4.5% / Sweet flavors of candied pineapple, peach, and apricots. Dry and effervescent.
$14/4pk

EVIL WATER - BLUE RASPBERRY
Hard Seltzer / 4.5% / A play off one of our favorite sour IPAs, What Even Is Blue Raspberry Anyway? Stone-fruity with notes of candied raspberry. Open gently, enjoy very cold.
$14/4pk

🌿All new releases drop Friday at 12pm at Ridgewood & 2pm at DUMBO.
🌱New release preorders open Thurs at 5pm on the webshop, (link in bio). *Preorder for Rodgewood pickup only*
🪴All online orders must be picked up within 3 days. Proxies okay.
🌵Shipping available for residents in NY/PA/DC/NH.
🍃Orders placed from Thur-Sun ship out Mon. Orders placed Mon-Wed ship out Thur.

node.text:
We’ve gone nuts 🥜🌰

5 new beers drop today at noon! See all the details below:

NUTS 4 NUTS
Imperial Stout / 12% / Delicious NYC warm nuts flavors of honey roasted peanuts, butter toffee cashews, honey roasted almonds, and cashew crunch. Smooth, nutty, decadent.
$22/4pk

DUMB FRUIT 6 - BLACK CURRANT, PINEAPPLE, MANGO, COCOA DUSTED ALMONDS
Sour Ale / 6.6% / Smoothie-like notes of extreme sour black currant candy, overripe pineapple, sliced mango, and cocoa dusted almonds.
$24/4pk

NO PHANTASM NO CARE
Dry-Hopped Sour IPA / 7% / A delicious and well-balanced dry-hopped sour IPA brewed with real Sauvignon Blanc Must. No Phantasm here.
$20/4pk

GREENHOUSE HELLES LAGER CONDITIONED ON AMERICAN OAK FOUDRE
Helles Lager / 5% / Bright flavors profiles of freshly toast bread, drizzled honey, and herbs. Conditioned on American oak.
$14/4pk

I’M REALLY LOOKING FORWARD TO THAT CROSS-COUNTRY ROAD TRIP. EXCEPT I’VE FORGOTTEN HOW TO DRIVE.
Double IPA / 8.3% / Dry-hopped with Citra and Sabro hops. Distinct tasting notes of coconut, tropical fruit, & fresh squeezed OJ.
$20/4pk
